==English==
=== Etymology ===
The use as a proper noun stems from the use of [[Baloo]] as the name of a bear in [[w:Rudyard Kipling|Rudyard Kipling]]'s [[w:The Jungle Book|The Jungle Book]].  The character is simply named from the {{Hind.}} '''[[भालू]]''' (''bhālū'', bear).

=== Proper noun ===
'''Baloo'''

#A [[given name]] for animals.

